name: Units
label: Units
description: Standard Set of Unit definitions for the system

FLOW_DENSITY_PER_AREA.label: Flow Density per Area
FLOW_DENSITY_PER_AREA.description: Flow demanded by or discharged to a Water/Sewer network per area.

PIPE_DIAMETER_LENGTH.label: Pipe Diameter-Length
PIPE_DIAMETER_LENGTH.description: The diameter of a pipe multiplied by its length, used as a coefficient for pipe-infiltration calculations.

HEAT_FLUX_DENSITY.label: Heat Flux Density
HEAT_FLUX_DENSITY.description: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Heat_flux see description of heat flux density

MOMENT_DISPLAY_SCALE.label: Moment Scale
MOMENT_DISPLAY_SCALE.description: Display size of the linear moment

IN.label: in
IN.description: Exact, http://www.nist.gov/pml/wmd/pubs/upload/hb44-15-web-final.pdf, Appendix B. Section 3.1, Page B-10

FT.label: ft
FT.description: Exact, http://www.nist.gov/pml/wmd/pubs/upload/hb44-15-web-final.pdf, Appendix C. Section 2, Page C-4

YRD.label: yd
YRD.description: Exact, http://www.nist.gov/pml/wmd/pubs/upload/hb44-15-web-final.pdf, Appendix C. Section 2, Page C-4

CHAIN.label: chain
CHAIN.description: Exact, http://www.nist.gov/pml/wmd/pubs/upload/hb44-15-web-final.pdf, Appendix C. Section 4, Page C-8

MILE.label: mi
MILE.description: Exact, http://www.nist.gov/pml/wmd/pubs/upload/hb44-15-web-final.pdf, Appendix C. Section 4, Page C-8

US_SURVEY_IN.label: in (US Survey)
US_SURVEY_IN.description: 100/3937 Derived from the definition of us survey foot in terms of meters.  Exact, http://www.nist.gov/pml/wmd/pubs/upload/hb44-15-web-final.pdf, Appendix C. Section 4, Page C-9

US_SURVEY_FT.label: ft (US Survey)
US_SURVEY_FT.description: Exact, http://www.nist.gov/pml/wmd/pubs/upload/hb44-15-web-final.pdf, Appendix C. Section 2, Page C-4

US_SURVEY_YRD.label: yrd (US Survey)
US_SURVEY_YRD.description: Exact, http://www.nist.gov/pml/wmd/pubs/upload/hb44-15-web-final.pdf, Appendix C. Section 2, Page C-4

US_SURVEY_CHAIN.label: chain (US Survey)
US_SURVEY_CHAIN.description: Exact, http://www.nist.gov/pml/wmd/pubs/upload/hb44-15-web-final.pdf, Appendix C. Section 4, Page C-8

US_SURVEY_MILE.label: mi (US Survey)
US_SURVEY_MILE.description: Exact, http://www.nist.gov/pml/wmd/pubs/upload/hb44-15-web-final.pdf, Appendix C. Section 4, Page C-8

NAUT_MILE.label: nmi
NAUT_MILE.description: International Nautical Mile.  Exact, http://www.nist.gov/pml/wmd/pubs/upload/hb44-15-web-final.pdf, Appendix C. Section 2, Page C-4

TONNE.label: tonne
TONNE.description: Also known as a metric ton http://phyMETRICcs.nist.gov/cuu/pdf/sp811.pdf, Appendix B.

LBM.label: lb
LBM.description: Is Avoirdupois Pound.  Exact, http://physics.nist.gov/cuu/pdf/sp811.pdf, Appendix B. Footnote 22

GRM.label: gr
GRM.description: Exact, http://www.nist.gov/pml/wmd/pubs/upload/hb44-15-web-final.pdf, Appendix B. Section 3.2, Page B-10

YR.label: years
YR.description: http://physics.nist.gov/cuu/pdf/sp811.pdf, Appendix B. Year is 3.1536 E+07 seconds which is equal to 365 * 24 * 60 * 60

LB_MOL.label: lb-mol
LB_MOL.description: ASTM SI 10 standard SI1-.phhc8328.pdf page 29, 35 and http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mole_%28unit%29

ACRE.label: acres
ACRE.description: Exact, http://www.nist.gov/pml/wmd/pubs/upload/hb44-15-web-final.pdf, Appendix C. Section 4, Page C-9

US_SURVEY_ACRE.label: acre (US Survey)
US_SURVEY_ACRE.description: Exact, http://www.nist.gov/pml/wmd/pubs/upload/hb44-15-web-final.pdf, Appendix C. Section 4, Page C-9

BTU.label: Btu
BTU.description: Is IT BTU.  http://physics.nist.gov/cuu/pdf/sp811.pdf, Appendix B.  See foot note #9:

PA_GAUGE.label: Pa (gauge)
PA_GAUGE.description: Offset is one standard atmosphere in PA.  Offset is exact, See http://physics.nist.gov/cuu/pdf/sp811.pdf Appendix B.

KILOPASCAL_GAUGE.label: kPa (Gauge)
KILOPASCAL_GAUGE.description: Offset is one standard atmosphere (101325 PA) converted to kilopascal.  Offset is exact, See http://physics.nist.gov/cuu/pdf/sp811.pdf Appendix B.

MEGAPASCAL_GAUGE.label: MPa (Gauge)
MEGAPASCAL_GAUGE.description: Offset is one standard atmosphere (101325 PA) converted to megapascal.  Offset is exact, See http://physics.nist.gov/cuu/pdf/sp811.pdf Appendix B.

AT_GAUGE.label: kgf/cm² (Gauge)
AT_GAUGE.description: Offset is one standard atmosphere (101325 PA) converted to atmosphere-technical (AT).  Offset is exact, See http://physics.nist.gov/cuu/pdf/sp811.pdf Appendix B.

ATM.label: atm
ATM.description: Standard atmosphere, see AT for atmosphere-technical.  Exact, See http://physics.nist.gov/cuu/pdf/sp811.pdf Appendix B.

BAR_GAUGE.label: bar (Gauge)
BAR_GAUGE.description: Offset is one standard atmosphere converted to BAR.  Offset is exact, See http://physics.nist.gov/cuu/pdf/sp811.pdf Appendix B.

PSIG.label: lbf/in² (Gauge)
PSIG.description: Offset is one standard atmosphere (101325 PA) converted to PSI

TORR.label: torr
TORR.description: See http://physics.nist.gov/cuu/pdf/sp811.pdf Appendix B. for approx conversion and Table 11 for a reference to the exact conversion

MM_H2O.label: mmH2O (Conv)
MM_H2O.description: Millimeter of H2O Conventional, See http://physics.nist.gov/cuu/pdf/sp811.pdf Appendix B.

MM_HG_AT_32F.label: mmHg@32°F
MM_HG_AT_32F.description: See http://physics.nist.gov/cuu/pdf/sp811.pdf Appendix B.  Used centimeter of mercury (0 C) to pascal

FT_H2O.label: ft H2O (Conv)
FT_H2O.description: foot of H2O Conventional, See http://physics.nist.gov/cuu/pdf/sp811.pdf Appendix B.

IN_H2O_AT_32F.label: inH2O@32°F
IN_H2O_AT_32F.description: Inch of H2O at 32 Fahrenheit, Water is assumed to be in a liquid state. Equal to water at 0C.  No verified source

IN_HG.label: inHg (Conv)
IN_HG.description: Inch of HG conventional, See http://physics.nist.gov/cuu/pdf/sp811.pdf Appendix B.

PERCENT.description: Unit used to show a ratio as a percentage in the UI.

DECIMAL_PERCENT.label: decimal percent
DECIMAL_PERCENT.description: Unit suitable for storing a decimal number that represents an unspecified ratio.

GALLON.label: gal
GALLON.description: Exact, http://www.nist.gov/pml/wmd/pubs/upload/hb44-15-web-final.pdf, Appendix C. Section 4, Page C-11

MOL.label: mol
MOL.description: Where mol is the SI gram mol or gmol.

MONETARY_UNIT.description: For money of an unspecified denomination

BTU_PER_FAHRENHEIT.label: Btu/°F
BTU_PER_FAHRENHEIT.description: Exact, See http://physics.nist.gov/cuu/pdf/sp811.pdf Appendix B.8, page 46.
